            "code": "\t#Get ParamList\n\textensionTypeUUID \u003d self.session.custom.equipment.extension\n\tOperationParameterLists \u003d BlueRidge.HMI.CNCLoader.ParameterList.getAll(value)\n\tOperationParameterList \u003d next((v for v in OperationParameterLists if v[\u0027extensionTypeUUID\u0027] \u003d\u003d extensionTypeUUID),None)\n\tif OperationParameterList: \n\t\tOperationParameterListUUID \u003d OperationParameterList[\u0027key\u0027]\n\t\tOperationParameters \u003d BlueRidge.HMI.CNCLoader.EngineParameter.getAll(OperationParameterListUUID)\n\t\treturn OperationParameters\n\treturn value",
            "type": "script"
          }
        ],
        "type": "property"
      },
      "persistent": true
    },
